# Bootstrap template — start with every transient path ignored. A new example
# that produces a committed jellycell tearsheet should REMOVE the relevant
# line(s) below (usually /artifacts/ and /manuscripts/) so the rendered
# output can be committed for GitHub / jellycell-site pickup.
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
uv.lock
/cache/
/artifacts/
/data/
/manuscripts/
/engine-audit/
/reports/
